(121, 195, 'Medhad Nasser Chowdhury', '1990-05-16', 'Apartment A5, House 10, Road 01, Block D, Pallabi, Dhaka 1216', 'Apartment A5, House 10, Road 01, Block D, Pallabi, Dhaka 1216', '01744674270', 'medhad.nasser.chowdhury@gmail.com', '{\"0\":{\"degree\":\"M.S.C\",\"instname\":\"other\",\"instnameoth\":\"Coventry University\",\"cgpa\":\"1 (Distinction)\",\"major\":\"No data found\",\"minor\":\"No Data Found\",\"location\":\"UK\",\"pyear\":\"2015-08-31\"},\"1001\":{\"degree\":\"B.B.A\",\"instname\":\"other\",\"instnameoth\":\"North South University\",\"cgpa\":\"2.83\",\"major\":\"sadfas\",\"minor\":\"No Data Found\",\"location\":\"Dhaka\",\"pyear\":\"2013-12-30\"}}', '{\"0\":{\"title\":\"Manager - Brand Marketing\",\"company\":\"Jamuna Group\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\uf0b7 Designed the Strategic Plan in attaining GOAL 2021. \\uf0b7 Planned, directed and launched the first smart shopping mall app in Bangladesh. Jamuna Future Park App is the first phone app with an indoor 3D map navigation system. \\uf0b7 Complete digital planning encompassing GDN, Instagram, Website, App, Youtube and Facebook. Pretty much introduced Digital Marketing to the Brand. \\uf0b7 Hosted 67 events and activations from diverse genres in a span of 11 months. \\uf0b7 Creative Brains behind all the JFP TVC, OVC, Event, Magazines and E \\u2013 commerce Website.\",\"joinedin\":\"2019-03-24\",\"leftin\":\"2020-04-25\"},\"1001\":{\"title\":\"Deputy Manager - Marketing\",\"company\":\"Rise Group\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\u2022 Led both the brand and sales team towards the short term goals of the both the companies. \\u2022 Built communication campaigns in both the online and offline channels in order to penetrate the heavily saturated industry. \\u2022 Introduced a complete digital business model for the properties company. \\u2022 Developed effective BTL events among the target niche in order to patronize their high involvement decision making process\",\"joinedin\":\"2019-02-25\",\"leftin\":\"2019-03-21\"},\"1002\":{\"title\":\"Senior Strategic Planner\",\"company\":\"Concord Group\",\"responsibilites\":\"Developed a marketing plan (1 year operational and 5 year strategic) for the brand Xtreme Racing - Go kart with successful implementation and returns. \\uf0b7 Strategic development of communication plans for both offline and online platforms including both ATL and BTL advertising Medias. \\uf0b7 Research based development of strategic moves in order to form joint ventures\\/alliances with prospective corporate brands. \\uf0b7 Development of digital campaigns for the brand along with coordinating with Advertisement Agency generating the most plausible productive execution. \\uf0b7 Keeping market intelligence along with the happenings in both the automobile industry and the market to generate financially feasible creative ideas \\uf0b7 Planning and executing all regular and newly built events targeting both B2C and B2B customer base.\",\"joinedin\":\"2016-06-02\",\"leftin\":\"2018-12-31\"},\"1003\":{\"title\":\"Apprentice Strategic Planning\",\"company\":\"Carrotcomm Ltd.\",\"responsibilites\":\"Managing clients and vendors through constant communication with various hierarchies of employees at both ends. \\uf0b7 Ensuring execution of communication strategy from the brainstorming part to the end tangible deliverables outcome. \\uf0b7 Managing events and activations in accord to the creative plan with high input of Human capital vested in action. \\uf0b7 Preparing creative and client brief; pitching briefs to two different set of perceptions and ensuring proper documentation of work.\",\"joinedin\":\"2013-10-17\",\"leftin\":\"2014-01-28\"},\"1004\":{\"title\":\"Executive - BTL Planning\",\"company\":\"NGe inc.\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\uf0b7 Development, production and delivery of projects from proposal right up to delivery. \\uf0b7 Delivering events on time, within budget, that meet (and hopefully exceed) expectations. \\uf0b7 Setting, communicating and maintaining timelines and priorities on every project. \\uf0b7 Communicating, maintaining and developing client relationships. \\uf0b7 Providing leadership, motivation, direction and support to your team. \\uf0b7 Being responsible for all project budgets from start to finish.\",\"joinedin\":\"2006-12-10\",\"leftin\":\"2012-10-31\"}}', '{\"0\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/the7marketeers.wixsite.com\\/digitalmarketing\",\"comment\":\"Digital Marketing educational website\"},\"1001\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/play.google.com\\/store\\/apps\\/details?id=com.jamunafuturepark&hl=en\",\"comment\":\"Jamuna Future Park App. The first smart shopping mall app in Bangladesh\"}}', 'Working as a brand strategist is actually part of something I cherish in Life. I have been a marketing fanatic since my sophomore years in North South University. I pursued a MSc in Strategic Marketing from UK to add more value to my path to be a crazy marketer. With a hefty experience of more than 10 years in the brand development sector I vouch myself to be an expert at brand image re-animation.\r\n\r\nManaging brands in the digital era has also allowed me to row into app based marketing, google display network and influence marketing. Planning with a clear vision encompassing feasibility has always been my stronghold. On the flip-side creativity combined with concrete consumer insight has aided my small but impact-full advertisement career. \r\n\r\nThus I try sticking to jobs that lets me research, implement and lastly take accountability in the brand development sector.', 'M.S.C', '1 (Distinction in Masters Research)', '{\"0\":{\"achieve\":\"IELTS SCORE: \\r\\nOverall Score: 7.5\\r\\nSpeaking  8 \\r\\nWriting 7\\r\\nListening 8\\r\\nReading 7.5\"},\"1001\":{\"achieve\":\"\\uf0b7 1st Runner-up in National Undergraduate Advertisement Contest called Ad-maker\\r\\nBangladesh 2012 (Intra level)\\r\\n\\uf0b7 4th position in National Undergraduate Advertisement Contest called Ad-maker\\r\\nBangladesh 2012 (Inter level).\\r\\n\\uf0b7 Full time vocal in four music albums released from Fahim Music, Laser Vision, X Audio\\r\\nand T.A.\"}}', '{\"0\":{\"competent\":\"Leadership Skill\"},\"1001\":{\"competent\":\"Planning Skill\"},\"1002\":{\"competent\":\"Budget Management Skill\"}}', 'A marketing veteran with relevant experiences of working as a Strategist, who utilizes creativity,\r\nleadership and teamwork to design and solutions that create customer value. Being part\r\nof a wide range of brand planning campaigns, I vouch myself to be Confident, Innovative and\r\nVersatile. Currently seeking a brand managerial position in a technologically driven business design in order to exercise my core competencies within the paradigm shift currently taking place in the Bangladesh business scenario.', '{\"0\":{\"title\":\"Arif Nawshad\",\"company\":\"Concord Group\",\"contactinfo\":\"01913531381\"},\"1001\":{\"title\":\"Dr. Mohammad Alamgir\",\"company\":\"Jamuna Group\",\"contactinfo\":\"01819269800\"}}', 'careerfile/1587826737.pdf', 'Dhaka', '2020-04-25', '30', 'Male', 'BM0825586', 'Unmarried', '2020-04-25 20:58:57', '2020-04-25 20:58:57', ''),
