(159, 261, 'Md. Mizanur Rahman', '1993-01-10', 'House #481, Holding #03, Vill: Beara, P.O: Aulia Nagar, P.S: Trishal, Mymensingh – 2222', 'House #481, Holding #03, Vill: Beara, P.O: Aulia Nagar, P.S: Trishal, Mymensingh – 2222', '01633050870', 'mizanrahman.bsc@gmail.com', '[{\"degree\":\"B.S.C\",\"instname\":\"other\",\"instnameoth\":\"Daffodil International University (DIU)\",\"cgpa\":\"3.91 Out of 4\",\"major\":\"fgsdfg\",\"minor\":\"undefined\",\"location\":\"Dhaka, Bangladesh\",\"pyear\":\"2018-12-31\"}]', '{\"0\":{\"title\":\"Assistant Hydro-graphic Surveyor\",\"company\":\"Hyundai Engineering & Construction Co., Ltd.\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\u2022 Preparing and maintaining CAD drawing from sketches, maps, reports, verbal instructions and legal descriptions of surveys in order to describe, certify and liability for work performed.   \\u2022 Coordinate finding with the work of engineering and clients and adjust surveying instruments in order to maintain their accuracy.   \\u2022 Supporting the project team in the design process to estimate cost limits, quality, safety and budget for new design.   \\u2022 Checking day to day log sheet, writing report and supervise the defined work area and staff.\",\"joinedin\":\"2019-09-05\",\"leftin\":\"2020-09-05\"},\"1001\":{\"title\":\"Executive Engineer\",\"company\":\"Minister Hi-tech Park Ltd.\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\u2022 Supervising the work of the technicians listed by Minister Hi-tech Park Ltd. and submitted bills through verification\\u2019s.   \\u2022 Occasionally visit divisional service centers and arranged standard service to solve all customer problems & to develop a balanced dealer network.   \\u2022 Attend meetings to rectify the faults to regarding quality assurance and take necessary steps to make correction.   \\u2022 Any task given by management had to perform carefully.\",\"joinedin\":\"2018-09-01\",\"leftin\":\"2019-08-31\"}}', '{\"0\":{\"url\":\"Home security system with PCB design.\",\"comment\":\"This home security monitoring project is a simple home security project that will trigger a buzzer when the magnetic contact is opened. Magnetic contacts are usually NC (Normally Closed) and are used on doors and windows. They consists of two parts namely a magnet and a reed switch. When the reed switch is in close proximity to the magnet, the switch will close and vice versa. when the door is closed, the two parts are in close contact and hence the switch is closed. When the door is opened, the magnet will be a distance away from the reed switch and hence the switch will open.\"},\"1001\":{\"url\":\"Fire detection with PCB design.\",\"comment\":\"Fire detection project is a simple fire alarm circuit based on a Light Dependent Resistor (LDR) and lamp pair for sensing the fire. The alarm works by sensing the smoke produced during fire. The circuit produces an audible alarm when the fire breaks out with smoke. When there is no smoke the light from the bulb will be directly falling on the LDR. The LDR resistance will be low and so the voltage across it (below 0.6V). The transistor will be OFF and nothing happens. When there is sufficient smoke to mask the light from falling on LDR, the LDR resistance increases and so do the voltage across it. Now the transistor will switch to ON.\"}}', 'I have a Bachelor’s degree in Electrical & Electronic Engineering with my solid experience. I bring real life experience leading multi-disciplinary teams while delivering actionable solutions in the form of Data Entry and well capable documentation with MS Word, MS Excel etc., overall campaign effectiveness, segmentation, and insights. \r\n\r\nI have vast experience about IT related works and relevant education. In brief, I have 2 years of experience as an Executive Engineer with Minister Hi-tech Park Ltd. and an Assistant Hydro-graphic Surveyor with Hyundai Engineering & Construction Co., Ltd. I have gained experience in both supervising and working along with the factory teams and I am aware that I will be offering the same amount of excellence in the same capacity to your organization. \r\n\r\nIn support of my application I have attached a copy of my Resume. It shows that I will bring important skills to the position, including:\r\n          • Able to work under pressure\r\n          • Proactive and can-do attitude\r\n          • High-level customer service\r\n          • Product Research & Development\r\n          • Troubleshooting & Operation\r\n\r\nI would request you to get in touch with me for an interview. You can call me at any time of the day at +880 1633-050870 or email me at mizanrahman.bsc@gmail.com at your convenience. I am waiting for a response from your side as soon as possible.', 'B.S.C', '3.91', '[{\"achieve\":\"Saved 7.5% cost of company by root plane and duty roster on Car driver and Boat captain at Hyundai Engineering & Construction Co., Ltd.\"}]', '[{\"competent\":\"MS Word, MS Excel, MS PowerPoint, AutoCAD, Proteus, OrCAD, MATLAB, LAN\\/WAN Technology.\"}]', 'With the belief “There is always a better way of doing works”, I want a highly rewording career to help organizations maximize productivity, profitability & quality by focusing economy and safety where in addition to my 2 years of professional experience, The entire personal management, Meeting project target and Job responsibilities will be invaluable. I am an effective communicator with the ability to provide leadership in teams.', '{\"0\":{\"title\":\"Md. Saiful Islam (Rony), Deputy Manager\",\"company\":\"Minister Hi-tech Park Ltd.\",\"contactinfo\":\"Mobile: +880 1642-229019; Email: myoneservice01@gmail.com\"},\"1001\":{\"title\":\"Mrs. Sharmin Ahmed, Senior Lecturer\",\"company\":\"Daffodil International University\",\"contactinfo\":\"Cell: +880 1717-638029; Email: sharmin.eee@diu.edu.bd\"}}', 'careerfile/1606579985.pdf', 'Mymensingh', '2020-11-28', '27', 'Male', 'NID: 7336849448', 'Unmarried', '2020-11-28 22:13:05', '2020-11-28 22:13:05', '');
