d checklist for vehicle maintenance. \\u2022\\tMonitoring strict servicing and maintenance times to minimize downtime and maintain schedules. \\u2022\\tRecruiting & monitoring driver behavior and ensuring a high level of customer service. \\u2022\\tUtilizing GPS systems to monitor drivers and track vehicles in case of theft. Major Achievement: \\u2022\\tPrepared transport policy for Recon engine distribution in rebuild workshops. \\u2022\\tReduced 11.5% of vehicle maintenance cost by tracking and fixing the proper service schedule. \\u2022\\tSaved 16% of fuel consumption by checking vehicle Logbooks on day-to-day basis. \\u2022\\tUpdating of vehicle documents on time, resulting no off-road vehicles due to lack of documents\",\"joinedin\":\"2020-09-01\",\"leftin\":\"2021-05-09\"},\"1001\":{\"title\":\"Product Manager (After-sales service)\",\"company\":\"Nitol Motors Ltd.\",\"responsibilites\":\"\\u2022\\tProviding Technical Support on Medium & Heavy commercial vehicles (M&HCV) segment.                                                                                                                                    \\u2022\\tCollect, analyze, and interpret customer feedback for product development. \\u2022\\tCoordinate with TATA motors representative regarding product failure & development, warranty claim, complaint related queries, approval, advice and suggestions. \\u2022\\tDefining and Planning Product Strategy and Product Performance Analysis. \\u2022\\tTrain employees (technicians\\/engineers) about new products and skill. \\u2022\\tCo-ordinate with spare parts team for maintaining parts ability. \\u2022\\tExecute vehicle performance trial of new and existing model & conducting necessary testings.  \\u2022\\tInvestigating and solving problem like mechanical failure, electrical failure. \\u2022\\tCheck and judge all complaints and claims related to Medium & Heavy commercial vehicles. \\u2022\\tAttend all warranty claim related complaints in Medium & heavy commerc